AcmeTelecom Billing System
Ramie Al-Omari, Daniel Cooke, Jonathan Evans, Javad Moghisi

IntelliJ
--------
Install gradle
Install the gradle plugin in Intellij, set GRADLE_HOME in preference->gradle and restart. On osx with homebrew GRADlE_HOME should look like /usr/local/Cellar/gradle/1.0-milestone-5/libexec
Generate IntelliJ files ./gradlew cleanidea idea
Open the newly generated files in IntelliJ
Go to the gradle plugin tab (if its not there check the plugin is installed, GRADLE_HOME is set correctly and try restarting again)
Press on refresh to refresh the project / task list
Double click a task to run it

Command Line
------------

If you have gradle installed:
gradle <task>

If you dont have gradle installed (e.g. on doc machines)
Linux/OSX: ./gradlew <task>
Windows: gradlew.bat <task>

e.g.

List tasks:
gradle tasks

Build:
gradle build

Run:
gradle run


Running FitNesse
java -jar lib/fitnesse.jar -d fitnesse -e 1 -p 8080
